race.description: Rock At The Races 21 March 2026 Midway Handicap
race.comment: MAILATA (2) held up in the straight when resumed with a sound fourth behind Lyles over 1000m at Warwick Farm in BM72 class. Form has since been franked and can launch over the top of these. DETENDU (7) visors go on after sitting up on the pace with the 61kg when a gritty third at Hawkesbury first-up. Comes to hand quickly and shapes as the main danger. LEANTOTHEMOON (9) trained locally and liked the way she attacked the line first-up when third over 900m at Newcastle. Well drawn and has each-way claims with Gibbons retaining the ride. PEARLS TREASURE (10) mare resuming with a tidy record. Went out a winner at Scone and wasn't asked to do much in her two trials. Market watch with the claim.
